'''Bray''' ke  motsana o o  mo kgaolong ya Kgalagadiborwa mo [[Botswana]]. Motsana o, o na le baagi ba ka nna sekete mo nakong ya gompieno (1000). Go ya ka maduo a palo ya batho e e dirilweng ka ngwaga wa 2011, baagi ba motse o ba ne ba le makgolo a a 1,041.<ref>{{cite web
 | url=http://www.cso.gov.bw/media/2011%20Census%20_Alphabetical%20Index%20_Population%20of%20Villages.pdf
 | title=2011 Botswana Population and Housing Census}}</ref> Motsana o, o ka nna dikhilomithara di le masome a mane go tswa mo motseng wa Werda ntlheng ya botlhabatsatsi. Bontsi jwa banni ba motse o bo bua puo ya Sengologa.

==Botshelo jwa batho ba Bray==
Baagi ba motsana wa Bray ka bontsi ke barui. Ba ruile dikgomo, dipudi, dinku le dipitse. Fa gongwe ba a tle ba leme le ntswa ba fufegelwa ke mmu wa kgaolo ya bone o o seng monate thata go ka ntsha dijalo tse di nonofileng. O ka fitlhela gantsi ba lema dijalo tse di seng thata go mela jaaka magapu, mmidi le dinawa. Leruo la batho ba motse o le lentle thata e bile le kgatlhegelwa ke batho ba metse e e mabapi le one. Batho ba a tle ba etele teng go ya go reka leruo.

